== 發行 ==
《告密者》於2014年10月10日在北美各大戲院上映<ref name="Release" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115609&utm_medium=  twitter&utm_source=twitterfeed |title=Kill the Messenger, Starring Jeremy Renner, is Coming in October |work=Comingsoon.net |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archive-date=2014-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101084207/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115609&utm_medium= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《告密者》上映後獲得了多為正面的評價，在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於88條評論，持有75％的新鮮度，平均得分6.8／10<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_the_messenger_2015/ | title=Kill the Messenger | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=2014-10-22 | archive-date=2014-10-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022081442/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_the_messenger_2015 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據33位影評家，得分60（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/kill-the-messenger | title=Kill the Messenger Reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2014-10-11 | archive-date=2022-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112110704/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/kill-the-messenger | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在[[imdb|imdb]]上則得分7.3<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1216491/ | title=Kill the Messenger Reviews | work=[[imdb|imdb]] | publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] | accessdate=2014-10-10 | archive-date=2021-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226181130/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1216491/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

